Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fits snugly in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Wh-Wh-What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I can carry him in my arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if he's shorter than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...like Otani.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:48.57,Title,,80,0,85,,A Maiden's Determination! Love-Love Confession Plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you? Feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have come to the seaside for Umibouzu's live concert, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I even brought my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and be night time already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming to the beach during summer vacation should be about love and youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Love! Romance! Not Umibouzu, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're still trying to hide it at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just admit it to me and I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You llike Otani-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You like him, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boys and girls, please listen up for a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:03:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's try to give Risa and Otani-kun some alone time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of Risa realizing her one-sided love, we all need to do what we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What the heck are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're finally going to confess to Otani-kun, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, everyone already knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who hasn't realized it is Otani himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.34,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you for ages...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:42.15,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Everyone is so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Nothing at all, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? My turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! This is nothing like the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:05.61,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch, Suzuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi... look, a hermit crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, it hid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:22.76,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Suzuki-kun, let's have a race from the beach to the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:36.61,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all watching my every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.11,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get together... Get together... Get together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you so stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are casual, completely oblivious to other people's problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that! That's payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch our stuff. You guys go and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Risa will get bored all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun, could you stay with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tha... That's... I'll be fine by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're hurt. We can't just leave you on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My main objective for the day is to catch some rays anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well in that case, stay with Risa and you guys can both get a tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I'll be fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if you tan that skinny body of yours, you won't look any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're got this much time to spare, why don't you go swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's like that, huh? Let's go, Nakao, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I become a lawyer, I'm gonna sue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to swim with Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:19.58,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too... with Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to get him to sue you?! I told you to confess to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya wanna have some fun together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You really thought someone was trying to pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Resting, resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that was for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drink 'em both.\N Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why didn't you put it over there, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's fault is that? You're the one who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just returning the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for treating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just being quiet or are you feeling weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I've been wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get you some pain killers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You only just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I happened to accidentally fall for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such disgusting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything better we can talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With someone like you, there probably isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get your hopes up about ever finding a boyfriend, amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm just a giant amazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun, what did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! She just suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault. I'm just an amazon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You said a mean thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! She's the one who's always calling me a midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi really is weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl in love will always be emotional!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone you like, Koizumi? Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're denser than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.27,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.34,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:36.74,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.61,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I said {\i1}Hey{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me! What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go get snow cones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Stop ignoring me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your foot okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to an Umibouzu concert, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about the pain ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what was all that about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The summer sun was just too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's this guy you like Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Everyone else knows. You're gonna leave me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy you like is shorter than you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you cried when I called you an amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you let stuff like that worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own charm, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be indecisive. Just go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I mind, being the only one who doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is just the type of guy he is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is the type of girl I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "soon enough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I really do care, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.64,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if it'll go smoothly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but I like him and I just can't help it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The concert is about to start. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As punishment for making me cry, take a picture with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be indecisive. Just go for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just wait, Otani!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I never thought he'd be this slow on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been asking me,\N "Who does Koizumi like?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over since we got back from the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, don't forget that Otani-kun is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer vacation is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once summer is over, we've got the school trip and a ton of events coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep procrastinating, you'll have to deal with a ton of rivals going after Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! No, no no! I can't deal with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. I'll help you, but you need to do your best too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely useless using a subtle approach with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to do it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll never work if you can't even say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I just have to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, you need to get him alone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone? Just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it'd be your first time alone with Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Up till now, we've jsut been together as All Hanshin-Kyojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we get a romantic mood going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible or not, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with being All-Kyojin forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,..."I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Let me write this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gyah"? What am I, a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's nothing! We weren't doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about so secretively?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna say "right."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go no. Do it now, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:13:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're excluding me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I just have to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Disgusting"?! I was trying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I've got to say to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone keeps talking about it behind my back. It's really getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one who doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's because...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's completely useless using a subtle approach with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're the one I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I possibly say that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.43,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.16,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear what I just said, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.56,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't say that! That's beyond embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have to do it over summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't tell him now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it, Risa. Go for it, Risa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just be brave and do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.68,Superscript,,0,0,0,,I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've said a lot of bad things up till now, but, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just being emotional. You're being downright suspicious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ughh... whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were shouting during the game too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you, we won today because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know since you weren't watching at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was watching you the whole time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were so cool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if something is really troubling you, you can always talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to help, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you really consider me that untrustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting so distant, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we All Hanshin-Kyojin partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you clutching at your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Can't I clutch at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really like him that much? This guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an idiot... but he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's shorter than me, but he's so sweet that I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the reason you've been coming to watch basketball...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...is because this guy you like is on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that freshman, Yamamoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's someone shorter than you, and he's on the basketball team, it has to be Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikeda is pretty short too....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that dense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Otani is seriously slow, and hopeless to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. It's not like it matters, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right! It's my birthday! I totally forgot for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are perky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already opening it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A fountain you can put on your bathroom wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Awesome! I'm super happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for tonight's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,,She's wanted one for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't understand her taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's calling to wish you a happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a message and told him it's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer, or he'll hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Me" Who's "me"? Stop trying to act cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You lookin' for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Free?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:51.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,Free
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.96,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Free! Free! Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, meet me on the roof of the big building next to the train station at 7pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The roof? Why there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, and wear what you wore when we went to the festival, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we meeting in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was that about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not nothing big, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look inside, would you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Umibouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. It's the premium edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's been signed. It's my most treasured possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you said you'd never give this away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I'm giving it to a fan like you, I think God will forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is the limited edition badge that came with the CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As a treat, I'm giving this to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are all just extras.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Extras?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's dark enough. It should be about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are fireworks today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this place last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling a bit better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been all frustrated and weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought watching the fireworks would cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's appropriate when watching fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But "fine feathers don't make fine birds," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. They sure are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...really do like Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's now, I think I can say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I confessed to the guy I like, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Sunk! The Worst Confession in History!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
